O

org.commonvox.insight.anomaly_detector - package org.commonvox.insight.anomaly_detector
This package fulfills requirements for an anomaly-detection package (for the mythical e-commerce firm "Market-ter") which identifies and logs any user's purchase that is found to be an anomaly (unusually high) in comparison to recent purchases made by those within the user's network of friends (please click here or scroll down for more detailed information).
